data.title: Clients — Suite Sound Labs
data.meta_description: Clients who have had music mastered at Suite Sound Labs mastering studio in Vancouver, BC, Canada. They have had gold and platinum records and albums; won Juno awards, West Coast Music Awards, WCMA, Break Out West Awards, East Coast Music Awards and many other accolades.
data.text:
Alphabetical by 1st name. This list hasn’t been updated in years, it’s more historical at this point. It spans the 20+ year history of the studio and 5 engineers. The instagram is updated all the time and the playlists above are updated every few months. If you don't see your name, feel free to ask me to update it and thanks again!
